{"tid":1598765,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【香城Online全民皆兵】呢幾日會上線嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-09-27T15:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T10:04:24.000Z","uid":88214,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"74d6c9e382071b5e81d0862f51b982f8e68e154f","tid":1598765,"uid":88214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T15:45:26.000Z","msg":"入得嚟嘅呢幾日都有心玩<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: purple;\">【香城Online】</span></em></strong></span><br />\n呢幾日太多活動，怪獸亦都好大機會會嚟攻擊我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以準備打機嘅你，無論你長期上線，單機定掛機，都想你睇睇以下內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民備戰：</span></strong></ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fdmZErs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfdmZErs.png&h=3a839113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><em>咩係全民備戰？</em></ins><br />\n備戰係講緊個心態同決心，當然每個玩家嘅能力同底線都唔同，有時亦要避免打架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但怪獸唔係善男順女，佢地唔同你開波嘅機會係零<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以玩家們必須對作戰做最好嘅準備，最壞嘅打算</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><ins><em>點解要全民備戰？</em></ins><br />\n一、 保護其他玩家，人愈多愈安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二、 前線扣咗血嘅玩家愈來愈多，必須有更多玩家加入<br />\n三、 比怪獸，甚至背後嘅幕後大佬知道我地未棄Game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><em>點樣備戰？</em></ins><br />\n下定好決心，就可以睇埋落去。全民備戰，以武抗暴！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民魔法：</span></ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42PgGEY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42PgGEY.png&h=1ae244c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怪獸嘅實力實在太強，過往嘅普通攻擊嘅作用唔大，導致好多玩家受傷／Offline。所以我地必須加入魔法元素，拉近兩邊嘅實力差距。以下係一啲魔法嘅參考資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><em>火魔法：</em></ins><br />\n類型：進攻、防守<br />\n應用：撒退時使用可以阻礙警察進攻速度，怪獸暫時對火魔法嘅對應方法仍然不足<br />\n攻擊力：高<br />\n門檻：高，各位自行判斷風險</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><ins><em>水魔法：</em></ins><br />\n類型：輔助<br />\n應用：加入顏料可阻擋警察視線；加入氣味屬性可大減警察士氣；加粉鋪地亦可減低警察進攻速度<br />\n攻擊力：低<br />\n門檻：低，有心預備就得，但除咗滅彈之外暫時未見玩家大規模使用</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins><em>光魔法：</em></ins><br />\n類型：輔助<br />\n應用：影響怪獸視線，或者提示其他玩家<br />\n攻擊力：極低，除非你支鐳射槍成舊火箭炮咁大，已被部份前線玩家所棄<br />\n門檻：低，但鐳射槍功率高會有風險</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><ins><em>土魔法：</em></ins><br />\n類型：進攻、防守<br />\n應用：組隊用彈弓可加強攻擊力；土魔法陣放地亦可用作路障減慢怪獸進攻<br />\n攻擊力：中<br />\n門檻：低，隨處可見</span><br />\n<br />\n其他：<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">蟲魔法（未解鎖）</span>等等<br />\n期待大家繼續解鎖更多新屬性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總之全民魔法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民皆兵：</span></strong></ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9sZMjrZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9sZMjrZ.png&h=3d7b6119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好喇好喇！都知未必個個做得起魔法師<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實除咗魔法師之外，【香城Online】都仲需要唔同兵種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><em>步兵：</em>幫手近戰打怪獸</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><em>盾兵：</em>用盾抵擋怪獸嘅遠距離攻擊</span><br />\n<em>弓兵：</em>遠距離攻擊怪獸<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><em>魔法兵：</em>利用魔法元素輔助玩家進攻／撤退</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><em>工兵：</em>即場製造武器同任何保護性物件</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><em>消防兵：</em>消除怪獸毒性攻擊</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><em>補給兵：</em>為前線玩家提供物資補給</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><em>醫療兵：</em>治療受傷玩家</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><em>哨兵：</em>為玩家提供一切即時情報</span><br />\n<br />\n其他：<span style=\"color: violet;\">援兵（法律支援）</span>，<span style=\"color: pink;\">運輸兵（車手／保姆）</span>等等<br />\n怪獸太強大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唯有全民皆兵，每個玩家都搵到個屬於自己嘅崗位，互相分工先可以確保各位玩家安全。不分兵種，全民皆兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span> <span style=\"color: gold;\">時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">以武抗暴</span> <span style=\"color: green;\">武運昌隆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de6a7b90e050e3a502fa95354a346a6b16a5337","tid":1598765,"uid":88214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T15:46:25.000Z","msg":"啲圖整咗好耐 希望多啲人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4adc0193bd105a57d9993c89bfd291a87b8e6372","tid":1598765,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T15:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xkLvL8O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxkLvL8O.jpg&h=a79e4b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v6yk8mO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv6yk8mO.jpg&h=0c2ca0be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0dpQz9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0dpQz9.jpg&h=1630d9c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FcJpQz9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.